title: I'm in Love with the Villainess
subTitle: Rei Ohashi, an overworked employee, passes away after which she is reincarnated as Rae Taylor, her favourite video game's heroine, and gets attracted to Claire Francois, the main antagonist.

title: Uncharted
subTitle: Recruited by Victor, street-smart Nathan steps into a race for the lost treasure of Ferdinand Magellan. However, a corrupt billionaire and an evil mercenary also have the same goal.

title: Alpha
subTitle: Keda, the young son of a tribe chief, is accidentally left behind, and must survive in the wilderness. He encounters an injured wolf abandoned by its pack, and the two form a bond.

title: After Earth
subTitle: A father-son duo crash-land on Earth, a millennium after an accident forced humans to evacuate the planet. With the father grievously injured, the son must put his life on the line to secure help.

title: The Woman King
subTitle: A valiant Agojie general goes through a journey fraught with trauma, unexpected motherhood and a terrifying war against the Oyo to become the &quot;woman king&quot; of Dahomey.

title: Captain Phillips
subTitle: Somali pirates attack the Maersk Alabama, a container ship, while it is on its course to Kenya. Richard Phillips, the captain of the ship, uses his wits to negotiate with them to save his crew.

title: The Unholy
subTitle: After a girl with hearing impairment envisions the Virgin Mary and regains her ability to hear along with other powers, a journalist unravels the truth behind this paranoia.

title: Sardar Udham
subTitle: Indian revolutionary Udham Singh seeks revenge on Michael O'Dwyer, Punjab's lieutenant governor, after his troops mercilessly kill hundreds of people in the Jallianwala Bagh massacre.

title: Jumanji: Welcome to the Jungle
subTitle: Four teens are transported into a magical jungle game, becoming adult avatars and must navigate challenges to return home safely.

title: Jumanji: The Next Level
subTitle: After Spencer goes missing, his team of confidantes comes back to Jumanji to go to the undiscovered regions and support him in escaping the world's most lethal game.

title: Venom: Let There Be Carnage
subTitle: Eddie Brock tries to revive his failing career by interviewing a serial killer, Cletus Kasady, who is on death row. When Carnage gains control over Cletus's body, he escapes from the prison.

title: The Equalizer
subTitle: Robert McCall gives up violence and wishes to lead a quiet life. However, brutal events force him to take up the fight for justice once again.

title: Monster Hunter
subTitle: Captain Artemis and her group of soldiers are pulled into a world where dangerous monsters and humans co-exist. Grappled by danger, they must find a way to escape with help from a mysterious hunter.

title: Mobile Suit Gundam: The Witch From Mercury
subTitle: A reserved student from a distant planet enters an elite academy where mecha duels and corporate agendas collide in a battle for power and survival.

subTitle: K, an officer with the Los Angeles Police Department, unearths a secret that could create chaos. He goes in search of a former blade runner who has been missing for over three decades.

title: Baby Driver
subTitle: When talented getaway driver Baby meets his dream girl, Debora, he chooses to leave his shady life behind. But when he is called in for one last heist with an unstable crew, things get dicey.

title: Miss Bala
subTitle: Gloria gets abducted by a group of criminals when she visits Mexico to meet her friend Suzu. Later, she uses her wit to survive in the cruel world of crime.

title: Daddio
subTitle: A woman takes a cab ride back home from the airport. En route, she unexpectedly has an insightful conversation with the driver regarding the important relationships in life.

title: Insidious: The Last Key
subTitle: Parapsychologist Elise Rainier gets thrust into returning to her eerie childhood home where she and her family have to fight a dangerous otherworldly entity.

title: White House Down
subTitle: When terrorists suddenly invade the White House, police officer John Cale springs into action to protect his daughter and the President of the United States.
Jackson Curtis, a discontented writer, battles against all odds to keep his family secure when a series of apocalyptic calamities threaten to decimate humankind.

title: Anaconda
subTitle: A documentary crew, who are on a mission to find a tribe named Shirishamas, help a snake hunter when they find him stranded. However, he forces them to risk their lives and hunt down an anaconda.

title: Anacondas: The Hunt for the Blood Orchid
subTitle: A team of researchers is in Borneo to find the blood orchid, a flower that could hold the secret to eternal life. However, the scientists run afoul of the jungle's deadly snakes.

title: Anaconda 3: Offspring
subTitle: Peter Murdoch, a wealthy man, funds a project wherein two anacondas are tested in a research laboratory. Later, a mercenary is hired to stop the snakes after they escape and go on a killing spree.

title: Anacondas: Trail of Blood
subTitle: When an experiment goes wrong, a genetically enhanced anaconda offspring is unleashed. Possessing the power to regenerate, it quickly creates panic and destruction.

title: Brightburn
subTitle: Tori and Kyle find a baby boy in a spaceship and adopt him as their own child, Brandon. However, after turning 12, Brandon learns that he has superpowers and begins to use them for sinister purposes.

title: Men in Black: International
subTitle: Agent M, a probationary member of the MIB, teams up with Agent H and uncovers a sinister plot that reveals a traitor in the organisation aiding an alien invasion.

title: Girls' Frontline
subTitle: In a future world ruined by war, robot dolls fight instead of people. A team of good robots battles evil robots that turned against humans.

title: Bloodshot
subTitle: A soldier who died on duty is resurrected and given superhuman abilities by the RST Corp. But soon he realises the truth about his past and his resurrection and sets out to get revenge.

title: CJ7
subTitle: Ti, a poor construction worker, struggles to provide basic education to his son Dicky. He finds an orb in the scrapyard and mistakes it for a toy. It turns out to be an alien with regenerative powers.

title: The Ugly Truth
subTitle: Abby, a lovelorn TV producer, finds herself in the midst of tests when she strikes a deal with her chauvinistic colleague, Mike, who wants to prove to her the accuracy of his relationship theories.

title: Afraid
subTitle: Curtis and his family are asked to install an artificial intelligence program in their house in a bid to test it. However, they soon begin to experience disturbing occurrences.

title: Fatherhood
subTitle: A widower embarks on an emotional journey while raising his daughter single-handedly despite encountering several hurdles along the way.

title: Salt
subTitle: CIA agent Evelyn Salt's life takes an ugly turn when she is accused of planning the assassination of the Russian president. However, she flees and sets out to prove her innocence.

title: Godzilla
subTitle: The fallout of a military nuclear test causes an iguana to mutate into a giant monster. Now this monster lays waste to cannery ships and New York city in order to feed and protect its brood.

title: Hotel Transylvania
subTitle: Count Dracula runs a high-end resort for monsters and is overprotective of his daughter, Mavis. When Johnny, a human, enters the hotel, Count Dracula tries to prevent Mavis from falling for him.

title: Hotel Transylvania 2
subTitle: Count Dracula is overjoyed to witness the birth of his grandson, Dennis. However, when Dennis shows no signs of being a vampire, Dracula tries to help him unlock his powers.

title: Hotel Transylvania: Transformania
subTitle: When Van Helsing's invention goes awry, Johnny turns into a monster and Dracula becomes human. Later, they embark on a journey to find a cure before their transformations become permanent.

title: Sisu
subTitle: As WWII comes to an end, Aatami Korpi trudges towards retirement with a bag full of gold. However, when a Nazi soldier learns about the treasure, he chases after the warrior, unaware of his prowess.
A spaceship crash lands on prehistoric Earth, leaving only two survivors. Soon, they must survive against the hostile terrain and vicious creatures.

title: Ghostbusters: Frozen Empire
subTitle: The Spengler family must join forces with the original Ghostbusters to stop an ancient evil force from refreezing the world, whilst protecting their iconic New York City firehouse headquarters.
